<plot>A Catholic Priest (Federico Castelluccio) agonizes over his involvement with a church parishioner and heavy contributor, Don Francesco Rinaldi (Michael DeNigris), head of a mob family trafficking in illegal substances. He is invited to the traditional Sunday pasta dinner with Don Francesco and the whole mob family to enjoy Aunt Millie's (Mary Ellen Ashley)celebrated Italian cooking. He is worried and reluctant to go and prays over it. He does go however and Paulie Goodman(Adam Mastrelli) gets them all over their heads In HOT WATER.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?261740</url></doc>
